### 1. 시스템 설정 조회
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/settings/system

### 2. 시스템 설정 수정 (JSON)
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/v1/settings/system
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiTime": "05",
  "playerTime": "01",
  "screenStart": "08:00",
  "screenEnd": "20:00",
  "playerVer": "1.0.0",
  "playerLink": "KUDIDPlayer.exe",
  "watcherVer": "1.0.0",
  "watcherLink": "konkuk_did_watcher.exe",
  "noticeLink": "campus_map.jpg",
  "introLink": "intro.png"
}

### 3. 시스템 설정 수정 - 필수 필드만
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/v1/settings/system
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiTime": "10",
  "playerTime": "05",
  "screenStart": "09:00",
  "screenEnd": "18:00"
}

### 4. 시스템 설정 + 이미지 업로드 (multipart) - 원자적 저장
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/v1/settings/system
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="apiTime"

05
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="playerTime"

01
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="screenStart"

08:00
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="screenEnd"

20:00
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="default-image.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test-image.jpg
--boundary--

### 5. [ERROR] 스크린 세이버 시간 형식 오류 → 400
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/v1/settings/system
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiTime": "10",
  "playerTime": "01",
  "screenStart": "9:00",
  "screenEnd": "20:00"
}

### 6. [ERROR] 필수 필드 누락 → 400
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/v1/settings/system
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiTime": "10"
}
